'''奇異國際LM500燃氣渦輪發動機'''，是[[奇異航空|奇異航空]]生產的工業和船用[[燃氣渦輪發動機|燃氣渦輪發動機]]，衍生自{{link-en|TF34渦輪扇發動機|General Electric TF34}}。目前版本的LM500可提供{{convert|6,130|shp|kW}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.geaviation.com/marine/engines/military/lm500-engine|title=The LM500 Engine PHOTO COURTESY OF REPUBLIC OF KOREA NAVY|publisher=GE Aviation|accessdate=2020-09-26|archive-date=2020-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200723214840/https://www.geaviation.com/marine/engines/military/lm500-engine|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在ISO標準下，[[热效率|热效率]]为32%<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.geaviation.com/press-release/marine-industrial-engines/ges-lm6000-demonstrates-outstanding-reliability-and|title=GE's LM6000 Demonstrates Outstanding Reliability and Availability in First Two Years of Commercial Service.May 23, 1995|publisher=GE Aviation|access-date=2020-09-26|archive-date=2021-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211112180158/https://www.geaviation.com/press-release/marine-industrial-engines/ges-lm6000-demonstrates-outstanding-reliability-and}}</ref>。

